\id 3JN - Capanahua NT -Peru 2008 (DBL -2013)
\h 3 JUAN
\toc1 Juaman raanni joi, jahuen quimisha sca
\toc2 3 Juan
\toc3 3 Jn
\mt1 3 JUAN
\mt2 Juaman raanni joi, jahuen quimisha sca
\c 1
\s1 Gayo qui jan siripi yohuanai
\p 
\v 1 Pastoro hihxon tah hen mihqui nea joi raanai, heen huetsa Gayon. Mihon tah hen shinancoinai.
\p 
\v 2 Min siripi jihuenon tah hen mihqui yocaxonai, heen huetsan. Min hisinyamanon tah hen yocarihbihi, miin shinan coshiscai quescarihbihi miin yora jascarihbinon.
\v 3 Neno nocoxon ta noquen huetsabaan hea yohirahsihiqui. Min jihuecoinxon sirijaquin shinanxon hahcai hea yohiquin. Papan joi min nincacoinai hea yohicanquin. Jaa nincacax tah hen hihti jenimahipiqui.
\v 4 Papan joi heen baquebaan nincacoinai honanax tah hen hihti jenimahi, heen jointiboyabi hihti jenimahi.
\p 
\v 5 Noquen huetsabo mihqui nocotaiya min jato yanapana ta hihti siri qui, heen huetsan. Min jisnima noquen huetsabo rihbi mihqui nocotaiya yanapana ta siri qui. Jascajacoin tah min jai.
\v 6 Min jatohon shinanai ta neno joxon noquen huetsabo rihbi yohihipicanaxqui. Jascapahbo mihqui nocorihbihiya jaya cati sca jato hinanrohayaxahnhue, noquen Papa hahxonaibo copi.
\v 7 Criston joi yohihi ta bocanihqui. Nincayosmabaan hinanah bi jahuabi bichintima ta shinancaniqui.
\v 8 Jaa copi tah non jato hinanti jai, hahbe yohinicabonoxon.
\s1 Diótrefes tiromahi jihuetai
\p 
\v 9 Papahon shinani jano tsinquitaibo qui tah hen quirica raanhohqui. Hen raanhoh bi ta Diótrefes jato tocan yohuan hihbocatsihxon jato nincamayamahiqui.
\v 10 Jaa copi tah hen jano caxon jan tiromahi hean shinanyaxihqui. Jan hehqui tiroma bi res yohuan yohuanai tah hen jaa shinanmayaxihqui. Tiromahi yohuanax bi ta yohuanti res queenyamahihqui. Noquen huetsabo jano nocotaibo bi ta jato mapemayamahiqui, janohahbo jaanbi Mapemayamanahue hahxon. Tsinquihihnataiboma qui ta jato camahihqui.
\p 
\v 11 Tiromabo jai quescayamahue, heen huetsan. Sirijaquin shinanax jihuehue. Sirijaquin shinanxon hahcaibo ta Papan baquebo qui. Tiromajaquin shinanxon hahcaibaan ta noquen Papa jisyamanishqui.
\s1 Demetrio siripi jihuetai
\p 
\v 12 Demetrio qui ta jatihibi siripi yohuanihqui. Jan Papan joiya hihqui ta honantihbiresi qui. Hea rihbi tah hen hahqui siripi yohuanai. Hen yohuani hihcoinai tah min honanrihbihi.
\s1 Hahan quirica queyoti
\p 
\v 13 Hicha mia yohiti shinanax bi tah hen quirica huishaxon yohiti queenyamahi.
\v 14 Mia jisi tah hen histon cacatsihqui. Jaatian tah hen mihbetan yohuantihi.
\p 
\v 15 Min jointi siripax jihuenon tah hen Papa yocacai. Nenoha noquen huetsabaan ta mihqui joi raanihqui, min jascabihi jayamahin noquen huetsan hahquin. Janoha noquen huetsabo jascajaquin rihbi yohixonhue jatihibi.
